Thank you for your interest in Columbia Biblical Seminary. Our goal is to equip you so that three qualities characterize you when you graduate:
– able to interpret and apply the texts of the Old and New Testament and to reason theologically from Scripture.
– able to maintain an intimate daily walk with Jesus and to help others grow in their relationship with him.
– able to engage in ministry that is culturally-relevant and promotes the worldwide proclamation of the gospel.
Join us and be equipped to impact the nations with the message of Christ.
